    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπί<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear>ν Διδύμῳ τῶι 

    <lb n="2"/>ἀδελφῷ χα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ί</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρε</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ν. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐκομισάμην <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὰ</supplied> γράμ-

    <lb n="4"/>ματα δι᾽ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὧ</unclear>ν γρά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">φ</supplied>εις τά-

    <lb n="5"/>χιόν μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear> ἀνέρχ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εσ</unclear>θαι. ἐ-

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>πειδὴ</corr><sic>επιδη</sic></choice> <supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">δὲ</supplied> <hi rend="diaeresis">ἴ</hi><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ιά μου ἔρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>α ἔ-

    <lb n="7"/>χω καὶ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ὔπω οὐδὲ ἓν <num value="1"/> 

    <lb n="8"/>τετέλε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">στ</unclear>αι, ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">να</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γ</supplied>καί-

    <lb n="9"/>ως σοι γράφω ἵνα εἰδῇς, 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐὰν μὲν φθάσω πρὸ 

    <lb n="11"/>τῆς τρύ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>ης <choice><corr>ἀνελθεῖν</corr><sic>ανελθιν</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="12"/>εὖ ἂν ἔχοι· ἐὰν δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὲ</supplied> μή, με-

    <lb n="13"/>τὰ τὴν τρύγην <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πά</supplied>ντως 

    <lb n="14"/>ἔρχομαι. ἐχά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied>ν δὲ 

    <lb n="15"/>πάνυ ὅτι ὁ φίλος <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied>ου αὖ-

    <lb n="16"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θ</unclear>ις τὴν χώραν αὑτοῦ 

    <lb n="17"/>ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>επλήρωσεν. τε-

    <lb n="18"/>τραλασον λέντιόν 

    <lb n="19"/>μοι πέμψον <hi rend="diaeresis">ἰ</hi>σχνὸν 

    <lb n="20"/>πρωτο<hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>φ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αν</unclear>ωτον· 

    <lb n="21"/>καὶ ἐὰν πέμψῃς, δώ-

    <lb n="22"/>σω τὴν τιμὴν τῷ Πε-

    <lb n="23"/>τεψόι. καὶ σὺ οὖν περὶ 

    <lb n="24"/>ὧν χρῄζεις παρ᾽ ἐ-

    <lb n="25"/><choice><corr>μοῦ</corr><sic>εμοι</sic></choice> ἐπὶ τοῦ παρόντος, μὴ 

    <lb n="26"/><choice><corr>ὄκνει</corr><sic>οκνι</sic></choice> γράφειν μοι ἡ-

    <lb n="27"/>δέως ποιοῦντι. ἄσπα-

    <lb n="28"/>σαι ἀπ᾽ ἐμοῦ τὴν σύν-

    <lb n="29"/>βιόν σου καὶ τὴν θυ-

    <lb n="30"/><choice><corr>γατέρα</corr><sic>θυγατεραν</sic></choice> καὶ τοὺς φιλ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οῦ</unclear>ν-

    <lb n="31"/>τάς σε πάντας. 

    <lb n="32"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι, 

    <lb n="33"/>ἄδελφε. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="34"/><expan>ἀπόδο<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> Διδύμῳ παρὰ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Σ</unclear>αραπίωνος. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.30714" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30714" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="201" type="textDate">III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.30714" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">971</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">30714</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">971</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0238;8;971" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30714" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30714" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div></body></text></TEI.2>